<TEI.2><text><body><div1 type="alphabetic letter" n="H" org="uniform" sample="complete"><entryFree key="Hoyday" type="main" opt="n"><orth extent="full" opt="n">Hoyday,</orth> an exclamation of contemptuous surprise: <cit><quote>h., a riddle!</quote> <bibl n="shak. r3 4.4.460" default="NO" valid="yes">R3 IV, 4, 460</bibl></cit> (most M. Edd. <emph>heyday</emph>). <cit><quote>h., spirits and fires!</quote> <bibl n="shak. tro 5.1.73" default="NO" valid="yes">Troil. V, 1, 73</bibl></cit> (Q <emph>heyday</emph>). <cit><quote>h., what a sweep of vanity,</quote> <bibl n="shak. tim 1.2.137" default="NO" valid="yes">Tim. I, 2, 137</bibl></cit>.
</entryFree></div1></body></text></TEI.2>